        <li><strong>Chats are always private — convert them if you want to share.</strong> Every Assistant chat is yours and yours alone, whether you're in Private space or a Project. Colleagues <em>never</em> see your chats. If there's analysis worth sharing, turn the chat output into an Editor document — that's the asset you can share with the team, not the thread itself.</li>
